\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F235222_135acadb2603a6c410e8e604e8eb6713.jpg&h=e6b5414a&s={SIZE}\" />呢個男人好似係日本殺人魔</blockquote><br />\n講緊Stairway to Heaven?<br />\n呢個講法最先係耶膠電視節目主持人提出嘅, 因為好多基要派耶膠都唔妥rock, metal, 話呢啲係撒旦用嚟迷惑人心引人墜落嘅音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要聽倒轉版可以去youtube搵, 我聽過就覺得所謂撒旦訊息連空耳都唔算, 可能真係要耶膠先聽得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7, 80年代美國耶膠當道嗰陣班耶膠到處咬人, 凡係唔啱耶膠道德標準嘅藝術, 娛樂都俾佢哋話喺撒旦作為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為啲rock, metal歌未必首首都係同宗教, 撒旦有關, 佢哋就諗出個解釋, 話呢啲歌就咁聽好似冇嘢, 其實班撒旦走狗已經加咗邪惡嘅訊息, 不過佢哋為咗唔俾人發現於是將訊息倒轉收埋喺首歌入面, 等普通人聽嘅時候人腦下意識掉轉首歌結果俾啲訊息洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThe Waitresses直頭寫咗首歌The Smartest Person I Know笑鳩班耶膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於Game方面幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31973c9ca9b13ae8659ba96873f90bf005912903","tid":365953,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T17:44:23.000Z","msg":"半夜三更嚇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996573a2503a5433a06a5b8dd783d8f521965b0a","tid":365953,"uid":74088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:04:06.000Z","msg":"有啲興趣，lm先"},{"pid":"11f8072cef1996b7002dc554aadb0b941a0d0e84","tid":365953,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:21:08.000Z","msg":"幾恐怖"},{"pid":"f118d2a45bdc29e6c62bad4ac3a53d089c399f9d"